evidence.text: The plaintiffs' motion for a preliminary injunction (ECF No. 28) is denied. The plaintiffs' motion for class certification (ECF No. 34) is denied.
Case Terminated without prejudice, with each side to bear its own costs and fees pursuant to Federal Rule of Civil Procedure 41(a)(1)(A)(ii).
